{"tid":1511263,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"急不及待好想快啲開學玩玩了","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T22:35:30.000Z","uid":116526,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"79bf9f1c3b5825064478c4e3bfae6405fd017d9c","tid":1511263,"uid":116526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"今年升高中，終於唔洗做低form 比人蝦啦！急不及待好想快啲開學玩玩了。今個暑假高左10cm 又瘋狂練大隻，再加埋高form 既身份終於可以蝦返人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗返起以前成日比人玩真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家唔好學啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.比人打開書包拉鏈掉書包出窗 啲野散到成個操場<br />\n2.千年殺<br />\n3.離開位比人倒廁所水落水壺<br />\n4.打波比人掉頭 掉Jer<br />\n5.同學成日唔小心倒瀉果汁，成身都係<br />\n6.happy corner<br />\n7.lunch time 比人一個波車落兜飯度無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8.掉我書包落垃圾桶 再掉垃圾倒水落去<br />\n9.去廁格比人掉濕左既廁紙入黎<br />\n10.倒水入底褲 笑我懶尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11.放生雞蛋入我書包<br />\n12.上PE堂換衫果時收埋我啲衫 影相再傳出去再笑我<br />\n13.係我坐低之前踢開張椅 係咁笑<br />\n14.係咁笑我青頭仔 jer 短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n15.分組永遠無人同我一組，做project 唔叫我<br />\n16.lunch 搵位坐低次次都話有人，一坐低啲同學彈開曬<br />\n17.行過成日都唔小心kick 低我，之後成個人誇過我<br />\n18.PE堂打波sip 我腳 <br />\n19.去廁兜一野拉低我條褲同底褲黎笑<br />\n20....唉 我都打唔落去啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 band 3"},{"pid":"3c6350a127c0f27860dc9b8e476b3194a1b0c22e","tid":1511263,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15dkGJn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15dkGJn.gif&h=baf9afac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aff7mJo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faff7mJo.jpg&h=4a2afc3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9b2955e77baa41ad5e6ef2cf65e4bf8e04a9f79","tid":1511263,"uid":2612,"like":0